$$\begin{pmatrix} \alpha\\ \beta\end{pmatrix} \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &amp;= \alpha + \beta \\
\varphi_2 &amp;= W \cdot (\alpha - \beta)
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta = (\varphi_1 , \varphi_2)
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为正常顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$前后行构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W = 
\begin{pmatrix}
&amp;W_n^0 &amp; &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; W_n^1 &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp;\ddots &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp; &amp;W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$"><h3>基本算法</h3><p><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG" display="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="9.359ex" height="5.43ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1450 4136.6 ### 基本算法

$$\begin{pmatrix} \alpha\\ \beta\end{pmatrix} \leftarrow \theta$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\varphi_1 &= \alpha + \beta \\
\varphi_2 &= W \cdot (\alpha - \beta)
\end{cases}
$$

$$\theta = (\varphi_1 , \varphi_2)
$$

where

- $\theta$初始化为正常顺序
- $\alpha$, $\beta$前后行构成的矩阵
- $W$为维度与$\beta$行维度相同的矩阵

$$
W =
\begin{pmatrix}
&W_n^0 & & & \\
& & W_n^1 & \\
& & &\ddots & \\
& & & &W_n^{\frac{n}{2}-1}
\end{pmatrix}
$$

ul.li: 为维度与行维度相同的矩阵
